data.description: This charming home boasts 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths, offering ample space for your family. The formal living and dining rooms seamlessly connect with an open kitchen, creating an ideal layout for hosting gatherings. Enjoy a fenced yard complete with a storage shed for your convenience. The spacious kitchen features a breakfast bar overlooking the backyard, perfect for casual dining. Built in 2007, this home features laminate flooring in the living areas and cozy carpeted bedrooms. French doors open to a generously-sized screened patio with a tiled floor, providing a great outdoor space. Act quickly as this property is competitively priced for a swift sale! Property is being sold AS-IS. Please do not disturb the tenants.
